    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "Dawnsilver weapons are slightly lighter than silver. A dawnsilver weapon is 1 Bulk lighter than normal (or light Bulk if its normal Bulk is 1, with no effect on a weapon that normally has light Bulk).",
